
========================================================
  GLIA Live — Linux with a built-in AI terminal assistant
========================================================

Your AI assistant is called  glia

  glia <request>        proposes a shell command (Enter = run)
  glia -d <question>    plain-text answer, no command
  glia-hardware          shows the recommended AI model for this machine
  glia -p <idea>         plans a project and writes its files (step by step)

The AI model is preinstalled - try right away:

  glia set the keyboard layout to italian

To install GLIA on this computer:  glia-install

Dangerous commands always require typing YES.
Project: https://github.com/micheleperani76/GLIA

